snippet.title: Live Coding: Minecraft custom plugin development (Day 1)
snippet.description: Support the stream: https://streamlabs.com/devdungeon In this stream we will continue setting up the custom Minecraft server from the last stream by refining the server configuration, installing and setting up plugins, and writing custom plugins to integrate with Discord.
